Title: A Photograph of the Couple Kinga and Hasan Abdul-Qader Hamdan Outdoors, 1970
Description.note: A black-and-white photograph of the couple Kinga and Hasan Abdul-Qader Hamdan outdoors in front of a tree. The wife Kinga is wearing a dress while her husband Hasan Abdul-Qader is wearing a suit and tie. Handwritten on the back of the photograph is this note "I attest that this is a photograph of the friend Hasan Abdul-Qader Hamdan from Ein Yabrud village with his wife Kinga from Spain. The photograph was gifted to me as a token of our friendship and fraternity on January 7, 1970."|~|صورة بالابيض والاسود لزوجان، اُخذت الصورة بمكان خارجي فيه شجر. وتظهر فيها الزوجة كينجا من اسبانيا وهي ترتدي فستان وزوجها حسن عبد القادر وهو يرتدي بدلة وربطة عنق. كُتب على ظهر الصورة :" أشهد ان هذه صورة الصديق حسن عبد القادر حمدان من قرية عين يبرود وصورة امرأته كنجا من اسبانيا وقد اهداها لي هذ الصورة على سبيل الصداقة والاخوة في تاريخ 7-1-1970
Series & Collection: The Ghassan Abdel-Qader Hamad Collection  | Ghassan Abdel-Qader Hamad Sub-collection 1: Photographs
Description (Eng): A black-and-white photograph of the couple Kinga and Hasan Abdul-Qader Hamdan outdoors in front of a tree. The wife Kinga is wearing a dress while her husband Hasan Abdul-Qader is wearing a suit and tie. Handwritten on the back of the photograph is this note "I attest that this is a photograph of the friend Hasan Abdul-Qader Hamdan from Ein Yabrud village with his wife Kinga from Spain. The photograph was gifted to me as a token of our friendship and fraternity on January 7, 1970."

Title: A Photograph of a Man in Front of a Shopping Centre in Kuwait, 1955
Description.note: A black-and-white photograph of a man in front of a shopping centre in Kuwait. A few of the shops appearing in the background are Omega, Forts, Damas, Roamer, and Morad Yousuf Behbehani. A car owned by the Gherballi Limited Company, electricity division is parked next to the man. Handwritten on the back of the photograph is this note "This photograph is for Abdul-Qader Hsain,Umar as-Silwady took him to the Omega shop in Kuwait at the newly opened street on January 2, 1955.|~| صورة لرجل بالابيض والاسود امام مبنى في الكويت يسمى "وميغا"، وكتب على المبنى ايضا "فورتس داماس رومر ومراد يوسف بهبهاني، اما السيارة التي يقف الرجل بجانبها فقد كتب عليها " الغربلي المحدودة شعبة الكهربا".  كُتب على ظهر الصورة "هذه الصورة الى عبد القادر حسين عمر السلوادي اخذه عند... الكويتفي الشارع الجديد في تاريخ 211955

Title: A Family Portrait at a Photo Studio
Description.note: A black-and-white family portrait taken at a photo studio. The old man holding a cane and a rosary on the right is wearing traditional clothes— qumbaz, hatta, and iqal. Next to him, a young man wearing an abaya, hatta, and iqal is holding a flower vase and the old woman on the left is wearing an embroidered dress (thobe), a traditional belt (shamla), and a head shawl.|~|بورتريه بالابيض والاسود لعائلة في استوديو، يظهر الرجل من جهة اليمين وهو يرتدي زي تقليدي " قمباز، حطة، عقال"، وبجانبه رجل اخر يرتدي عباءة وحطة وعقال ويحمل مزهرية ورد بيديه؛ اما الامرأة المسنة تظهر وهي ترتدي ثوب مطرز وحزام.
